<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Generar Reporte - Hospital Loayza</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap JS (al final del body) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    

    @section Styles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/GenerarReporte.css" />
}

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.8), rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x300/0066cc/ffffff?text=Reportes+Hospitalarios') no-repeat center/cover;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .main-container {
            max-width: 1800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .card-header {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            border-color: #0066cc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background-color: #004c99;
            border-color: #004c99;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            border-color: #6c757d;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom:hover {
            background-color: #545b62;
            border-color: #545b62;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .table {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .table th {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-top: none;
        }

        .table td {
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .no-results {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .export-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>


    
    <section class="hero-section"> 
        <div class="main-container"> 
            <h1>
                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-bar-graph">
                </i> 
                Generar Reporte
            </h1> 
            <p>Genera reportes administrativos sobre pacientes y citas para una mejor toma de decisiones en el Hospital Nacional Arzobispo Loayza.</p>
        </div> 
    </section> 
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="card"> 
            <div class="card-header"> 
                <h2><i class="bi bi-funnel"></i> Filtros de Reporte</h2> 
            </div> 
            
            <div class="card-body"> 
                <form asp-action="GenerarReporte" method="post" id="reporteForm"> 
                    <div class="row g-3"> 
                        <div class="col-md-6"> 
                            <label for="tipoReporte" class="form-label">Tipo de Reporte</label> 
                            
                            <select class="form-select" id="tipoReporte" name="TipoReporte" required> 
                            
                                <option value="">Seleccione un tipo...</option> <option value="pacientes">Pacientes Registrados</option> 
                                <option value="citas">Citas Médicas</option> <option value="estadisticas">Estadísticas Generales</option> 
                            </select> 
                        </div> 
                        
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label for="fechaInicio" class="form-label">Fecha Inicio</label> 
                            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="fechaInicio" name="FechaInicio" required>
                        
                        </div> 
                        
                        <div class="col-md-3"> 
                            <label for="fechaFin" class="form-label">Fecha Fin</label> 
                            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="fechaFin" name="FechaFin" required> 
                        </div> 
                    </div> 
                    
                    <div class="row g-3 mt-3"> 
                        <div class="col-md-6"> 
                            <label for="especialidad" class="form-label">Especialidad (Opcional)</label> 
                            <select class="form-select" id="especialidad" name="Especialidad"> 
                                <option value="">Todas las especialidades</option> 
                                <option value="cardiologia">Cardiología</option> 
                                <option value="pediatria">Pediatría</option> 
                                <option value="general">Medicina General</option> 
                                <option value="laboratorio">Laboratorio Clínico</option> 
                            </select> 
                        </div> 
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label for="estado" class="form-label">Estado (Opcional)</label> 
                            <select class="form-select" id="estado" name="Estado"> 
                                <option value="">Todos los estados</option> 
                                <option value="confirmada">Confirmada</option>
                                <option value="cancelada">Cancelada</option> 
                                <option value="atendida">Atendida</option> 
                            </select> 
                        </div> 
                    </div> 
                    
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4"> 
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary-custom me-2"> 
                        <i class="bi bi-search"></i> Generar Reporte 
                        </button> 
                        
                        <button type="reset" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"> <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Limpiar Filtros 
                        </button> 
                    </div> 
                    
                </form> 
            </div> 
        </div> 
        
        <div class="card"> 
            <div class="card-header"> 
                <h2><i class="bi bi-table"></i> Resultados del Reporte</h2> 
                
                <p class="text-muted">Ejemplo de reporte generado para pacientes registrados entre el 01/01/2025 y 31/01/2025.</p> 
                
            </div> 
            
            <div class="card-body"> 
                <div class="table-responsive"> 
                    <table class="table table-striped table-hover"> 
                        <thead> 
                            <tr> 
                                <th>ID</th> 
                                <th>Nombre del Paciente</th> 
                                <th>DNI</th> 
                                <th>Edad</th> 
                                <th>Fecha de Registro</th> 
                                <th>Especialidad</th> 
                                <th>Estado</th> 
                                <th>Acciones</th> 
                            </tr> 
                        </thead> 
                        
                        <tbody> 
                            <tr> 
                                <td>1</td> 
                                <td>Juan Pérez López</td> 
                                <td>12345678</td> <td>45</td> 
                                <td>15/01/2025</td> 
                                <td>Cardiología</td> 
                                <td>En proceso</td> 
                                <td> 
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary"> 
                                        <i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Ver Detalles 
                                    </button> 
                                </td> 
                            </tr> 
                            
                            <tr> 
                                <td>2</td> 
                                <td>María García Ruiz</td> 
                                <td>87654321</td> 
                                <td>32</td> 
                                <td>20/01/2025</td> 
                                <td>Pediatría</td> 
                                <td>En proceso</td> 
                                <td> 
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary"> 
                                        <i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Ver Detalles 
                                    </button> 
                                </td> 
                            </tr> 
                            
                            <tr> 
                                <td>3</td> 
                                <td>Carlos Mendoza Soto</td> 
                                <td>11223344</td> 
                                <td>28</td> 
                                <td>25/01/2025</td> 
                                <td>Medicina General</td> 
                                <td>En proceso</td> 
                                <td> 
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary"> 
                                        <i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Ver Detalles 
                                    </button> 
                                </td> 
                            </tr> 
                        </tbody> 
                    </table> 
                </div> 
                
                <div class="no-results" id="noResults" style="display: none;"> 
                    <i class="bi bi-inbox" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #6c757d; margin-bottom: 10px;"></i> 
                    <p>No se encontraron resultados para los filtros seleccionados. Ajuste los parámetros e intente nuevamente.</p> 
                </div> 
                
                <div class="export-buttons"> 
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary-custom" onclick="exportToPDF()"> <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf"></i> Exportar a PDF </button> 
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary-custom" onclick="exportToExcel()"> <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-excel"></i> Exportar a Excel </button> 
                
                </div> 
            </div> 
        </div> 
    </div>



</body>
</html>
